{"tid":93537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反侵陣營開始全面內訌，有色人種指謫女權是白人專利！","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T14:37:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f545d622d20691342ae35c0eabc8bb2b20dd5504","tid":93537,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"反侵的million women march已經開始內訌：有色人種參與者指責成個活動都是privilege white women feminism，將種族議題、性取向等其他議題censor掉。 <br />\n--------------------------------------- <br />\nGrace Hong is not surprised. A professor of Asian American and Gender Studies at UCLA, Hong says for decades, white women didn't have to consider any interests beyond their own because &quot;historically, the category 'woman' has, implicitly, meant white women.&quot; The call to put womanhood above all else, Hong says, is based on the idea that &quot;critique and dissent undermine a unity that's based on the lowest common denominator: Find the one thing everyone has in common.&quot; <br />\n<br />\nThe fact that the feminist movement was so white for so long, says Ashley Farmer, is the reason so many women of color steered clear of it. Farmer is a historian at Boston University, and concentrates on African-American women's history. She says women of color noticed when their interests and needs didn't get a full hearing. <br />\n<br />\n&quot;When we actually get down to representation or creating a list of demands or mobilizing around a set of ideas,&quot; Farmer says, &quot;it tends to be that white middle-class or upper-class women's priorities get put above the rest.&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/b0ind7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fb0ind7.png&h=f393aa1b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRace And Feminism: Women's March Recalls The Touchy History <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.npr.org/sections/codeswitch/2017/01/21/510859909/race-and-feminism-womens-march-recalls-the-touchy-history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fcodeswitch%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F510859909%2Frace-and-feminism-womens-march-recalls-the-touchy-history&d=VfU7UGqeyHdBUD1vc26TcaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=fe6bc437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.npr.org/sections/codeswitch/2017/01/21/510859909/race-and-feminism-womens-march-recalls-the-touchy-history</a>"},{"pid":"88dd3123c071d3638d8fabc128607afcd47b6e79","tid":93537,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"認真，除左白人女人，真係冇咩聽過黑人女人會講女權主義喎"},{"pid":"9345b0228ad64b29180d978339b5f3033d7bf9f9","tid":93537,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"好！<br />\n回教大戰女權撚！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326b60cb6839eb583f6c8de46f707829db5c81b6","tid":93537,"uid":51859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T19:15:07.000Z","msg":"毛魔最愛拉一派打一派，發動人民群眾了"},{"pid":"63895d1e57de7e09a300913d4bd1b083b54d19a3","tid":93537,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"所謂少數人<br />\n少數民族 人種 女權 同性戀 左膠<br />\n將佢地放埋一齊 就自然內訌"},{"pid":"98374f25d0f5da90390ff859dffdda61b09a99fa","tid":93537,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T21:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78b164066eb6b9a7f7fbeda08853bf21556ca6f","tid":93537,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016c9a3f7694442f06e9772052548830d01f8e71","tid":93537,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}